{"tid":1442440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【注意】721係一個人都未被起訴","createTime":"2019-08-11T03:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T07:42:59.000Z","uid":37528,"like":58,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"a92010039d3d30bdf29fe0714f1a7108d6e9a3db","tid":1442440,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:14:08.000Z","msg":"&nbsp;7 月21日元朗港鐵站發生襲擊事件，警方昨日公布拘捕多3名本地男子，涉嫌非法集結，案件被捕總人數增至27人。<br />\n警方指出，昨日（8 月 8 日）上午分別在打鼓嶺分區及落馬洲分區再拘捕兩名分別 33 歲及 60 歲本地男子，以及於下午在天水圍分區拘捕一名 44 歲本地男子涉嫌非法集結，他們現正被扣留調查。<br />\n721 元朗襲擊事件，被捕總人數增至27人，全部未落案起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n柒婆話我地玉石俱焚？我地破壞法治？<br />\n咁點解有人犯法要拉有人犯法唔使拉？<br />\n邊個帶頭破壞法治？<br />\n我地先係最愛香港最想香港好果班人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fee82e848070e982d812844e1b7dbaf6ed7cf1","tid":1442440,"uid":50894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e66c9e54ae62b78cb56b1493ef67841dd368f3","tid":1442440,"uid":293012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:19:17.000Z","msg":"Yes and push"},{"pid":"db5d07b36a81f02c28b623fc53d7c7a12d4dd299","tid":1442440,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:29:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府破壞香港法治</span></span>"},{"pid":"8e017fce05b4cfc8a6a7472e7770308862d5280e","tid":1442440,"uid":55233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:31:48.000Z","msg":"721 元朗恐襲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f9eef77392552695599c368cdfe6fe4a9